<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Van In zuon din kross lampi ka hawh a ngai,
 Zielo chu lamdang um lo;
 Kawtkhak vak chuh ken muthei ngei puong ka,
 Kross lampi chuh ka mansak chun.

[V2]
 Kross lampi'n In ei tun ding (2)
 Chieh kawma het chuh thil nuomtak ahi;
 Kross lampi'n In ei tun ding chu.

[V3]
 2. Kross bul a chun ka puokgik a kiemang tai,
 Lalpa ka muh tak ziekin;
 Lungthim zang takin lam ka hawh pan tai,
 Ka lunggil pakna lan a dim.

[V4]
 3. Thisan kitheh khum lampi ka hawh a ngai,
 Hukdampa lampi bawl chuh;
 Chunglam gamnuom a chun kalto thei leng,
 Thagau, Pathien tawh chenna ah.

[V5]
 4. Ka Lalpan kross lampi chuh A hawh masai,
 Kei di'n Kross chungah A thii;
 Pathien Belam No di'n lam hak ahi,
 Tu'n hinna lamthak ka mu ie.

[V6]
 5. Khawvel lampi chuh zinbang in ka tha tai,
 Achung hawhkit ngeilo di'n;
 Lalpa'n, Hung in, ei ti'n, In ka zuon tai,
 Kawt hawnsa a ei ngakna ah.</lyrics>
<title>THE WAY OF THE CROSS LEADS HOME</title>
<hymn_number>123</hymn_number>
</song>